# Edit 2026-02-12:
Adds alert messages;
To activate click "Add Alert"
-> Condition:select this strategy
-> Choose: "Order fills"
(NOT "Any alert() function call")

If you choose the wrong alert type, you will NOT receive the alert_loss or alert_profit messages.
